name: Robin Kent
text: Bought brand name Ashley Furniture scratch & dent sale furniture. Excellent choices in sets.

name: Anedia Reese
text: They try their hardest to make sure everyone gets fed sometimes it's a nice amount of food other times it's not so much but it's always their best and the best that they can do is greatly appreciated.

name: Curt Hencye
text: Great church that loves Jesus and shows it in tangible ways to anyone coming into their services and their local community! Pastor Joe teaches through the entire Word of God verse by verse with worship that draws us to The LORD!

name: Cathy Sanchez
text:
A family of believers who love the Lord and practice loving their neighbors as themselves.  The Pastor preaches the Word and the message of the gospel in spirit and in truth! And he leads the congregants to share the good news and show brotherly love to all.
Their food pantry is a beautiful blessing to many and they distribute food to all who come in need generously! A body of believers who live the gospel message daily!!!

name: Candy Vinson
text: People were great and friendly. Music was awesome with John the worship leader.  Pastor Joe gave an amazing sermon that truly touched me. I had been visiting many churches the last 5 years, and still looking for my home church, and I hope and pray I have found it. I am looking to serve where I'm needed, and hope to be able to serve here. Thank you Pastor Joe for the awesome preaching!

name: Phyllis Wallace
text: If you are looking at making any kind of resolution this year it should be to go to this church and learn the word of God.  Pastor Joe will read through the Bible with such passion you can't help but feel the spirit of the Lord.  The worship team will make you want to get up and sing the Lord's praises.  I look forward to going,  Wednesday night service and Sunday morning.  You won't find nicer people.

name: indigo05 Mullet
text: This is my church and I love everyone so much. Pastor Joe is the most amazing pastor I've ever known. I love all our other pastors as well. This is the most non-judgemental  church I've ever gone too. They are always there to help whatever the need and are an amazing asset to the community. There are many ministries reaching out to help others.

name: Melvin Smith
text: I personally attend church here and I do half to say that our pastor is one of the best in my book and the people that surround you are not just others but more like family. If your looking for a church to attend I highly recommend you stop by and see for yourself.

name: MR TAX
text: Very Good Service.  Everyone was very friendly.  Pastor Joe was excellent.

name: Rant story time With jamie
text: Totally great church people n staff are friendly, and their all about jesus. Great place to grow n christ they have good fellowship i would recommend this church
